caption:
@pepstonor’s story is one of power: shared power. 

For Pep, sport isn’t just about technique. It’s about showing up, backing yourself, and realising you can play a sport, even if you’ve never had it in your life before. 

“It gives me so much joy to see a woman realise that she can play sport.” 

That’s the power of padel. That’s the power of community. 

Head to the link in bio to check out Pep’s story with @glorioussport.
